channel.description:
Ok ever since i think wednesday i cant log in to a server, i have no idea why not, i can log into mine ok, but no one elses not even using no-ip or hamachi, when i try and use them it says:
[code]Error Connecting to server. Must be down Click "cancel" then "start server" to make your own.[/code]
now this makes no sence to me because its been find before and i am not making my own server :S
Need help alot please
Thanks PLease help Kilopy :):):):):):)

item.title: Some Reason No Server Working Now :s:S:s READ!
item.dc:creator: @Halo_Pk Halo_Pk
item.description:
@Halo_Pk wrote:

well i don’t believe there is a such thing of not being able to join a server just do the following

  1. while checking the server you are going to join find port # first thing
    most of the time it will be 43594
    2.some people use hamachi that is me ;D to make sure that it says if there hamachi take myne for instance halopkscape1-20 pass 123
    this means halopkscape1 is the network name to join and 123 is the pass the along with hamachi there is always an ip
    3.most people i notice dont use hamachi and will have a no-ip
    all you have to do is type in the ip this will be random tomscapeiscool.no-ip.org
    4.if this all fails then either the server is just down or your computer is a cookie head
    ~halopk
